## Objective
Implement the main routing and layout for viewing a specific instance's details.

## Requirements
- Create a new page component `client/src/pages/InstanceDetailsPage.tsx`.
- Add a new route `/instances/:id` in the frontend router.
- Use the API client to fetch instance details and sprint data on mount.
- Display basic instance information (Name, Version, Description, Stack).
- Handle loading and error states appropriately.
